file.name: azure.com-applicationinsights-webTests_API-2015-05-01-swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: Azure Application Insights client for web test based alerting.
  title: ApplicationInsightsManagementClient
  version: 2015-05-01
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - cloud
  x-logo:
    url: https://assets.onestore.ms/cdnfiles/onestorerolling-1606-01000/shell/v3/images/logo/microsoft.png
  x-origin:
    - format: swagger
      url: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Azure/azure-rest-api-specs/master/specification/applicationinsights/resource-manager/Microsoft.Insights/stable/2015-05-01/webTests_API.json
      version: "2.0"
  x-providerName: azure.com
  x-serviceName: applicationinsights-webTests_API
  x-tags:
    - Azure
    - Microsoft
security:
  - azure_auth:
      - user_impersonation
paths:
  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/providers/Microsoft.Insights/webtests":
    get:
      description: Get all Application Insights web test alerts definitions within a
        subscription.
      operationId: WebTests_List
      parameters:
        - description: The API version to use for this operation.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestList:
              value: 2015-05-01
        - description: The ID of the target subscription.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestList:
              value: subid
      responses:
        "200":
          description: A list of 0 or more Application Insights web test definitions.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/webTestListResult"
              examples:
                webTestList:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/webTestList"
      x-ms-pageable:
        nextLinkName: nextLink
  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Insights/components/{componentName}/webtests":
    get:
      description: Get all Application Insights web tests defined for the specified
        component.
      operationId: WebTests_ListByComponent
      parameters:
        - $ref: "#/components/parameters/ComponentNameParameter"
        - description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._\(\)]+$
          examples:
            webTestListByComponent:
              value: my-resource-group
        - description: The API version to use for this operation.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestListByComponent:
              value: 2015-05-01
        - description: The ID of the target subscription.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestListByComponent:
              value: subid
      responses:
        "200":
          description: A list containing 0 or more web test definitions.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/webTestListResult"
              examples:
                webTestListByComponent:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/webTestListByComponent"
      x-ms-pageable:
        nextLinkName: nextLink
  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Insights/webtests":
    get:
      description: Get all Application Insights web tests defined within a specified
        resource group.
      operationId: WebTests_ListByResourceGroup
      parameters:
        - description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._\(\)]+$
          examples:
            webTestListByResourceGroup:
              value: my-resource-group
        - description: The API version to use for this operation.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestListByResourceGroup:
              value: 2015-05-01
        - description: The ID of the target subscription.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestListByResourceGroup:
              value: subid
      responses:
        "200":
          description: A list containing 0 or more web test definitions.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/webTestListResult"
              examples:
                webTestListByResourceGroup:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/webTestListByResourceGroup"
      x-ms-pageable:
        nextLinkName: nextLink
  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Insights/webtests/{webTestName}":
    delete:
      description: Deletes an Application Insights web test.
      operationId: WebTests_Delete
      parameters:
        - description: The ID of the target subscription.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestDelete:
              value: subid
        - description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._\(\)]+$
          examples:
            webTestDelete:
              value: my-resource-group
        - $ref: "#/components/parameters/WebTestNameParameter"
        - description: The API version to use for this operation.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestDelete:
              value: 2015-05-01
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful request to delete a web test definition.
        "204":
          description: "No content: the request was successful, but the response is empty
            (the request to delete failed because the specified web test does
            not exist)."
    get:
      description: Get a specific Application Insights web test definition.
      operationId: WebTests_Get
      parameters:
        - description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._\(\)]+$
          examples:
            webTestGet:
              value: my-resource-group
        - description: The API version to use for this operation.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestGet:
              value: 2015-05-01
        - description: The ID of the target subscription.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestGet:
              value: subid
        - $ref: "#/components/parameters/WebTestNameParameter"
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Ann Application Insights web test definition.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/WebTest"
              examples:
                webTestGet:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/webTestGet"
    patch:
      description: Creates or updates an Application Insights web test definition.
      operationId: WebTests_UpdateTags
      parameters:
        - description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._\(\)]+$
          examples:
            webTestUpdateTags:
              value: my-resource-group
        - description: The API version to use for this operation.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestUpdateTags:
              value: 2015-05-01
        - description: The ID of the target subscription.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestUpdateTags:
              value: subid
        - $ref: "#/components/parameters/WebTestNameParameter"
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/TagsResource"
        description: Updated tag information to set into the web test instance.
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Updating the Application Insights web test tags was successful. Web
            test tags are updated and returned with the rest of the WebTest
            object properties.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/WebTest"
              examples:
                webTestUpdateTags:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/webTestUpdateTags"
    put:
      description: Creates or updates an Application Insights web test definition.
      operationId: WebTests_CreateOrUpdate
      parameters:
        - description: The name of the resource group. The name is case insensitive.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            maxLength: 90
            pattern: ^[-\w\._\(\)]+$
          examples:
            webTestCreate:
              value: my-resource-group
            webTestUpdate:
              value: my-resource-group
        - description: The API version to use for this operation.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestCreate:
              value: 2015-05-01
            webTestUpdate:
              value: 2015-05-01
        - description: The ID of the target subscription.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
          examples:
            webTestCreate:
              value: subid
            webTestUpdate:
              value: subid
        - $ref: "#/components/parameters/WebTestNameParameter"
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/WebTest"
        description: Properties that need to be specified to create or update an
          Application Insights web test definition.
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Adding the Application Insights web test was successful. Web test
            properties are updated and returned.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/WebTest"
              examples:
                webTestCreate:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/webTestCreate"
                webTestUpdate:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/webTestUpdate"
